title: 2017 Week 6 preview: The Zeke-less Cowboys, Wentz vs. Cam
itunes:title: 2017 Week 6 preview: The Zeke-less Cowboys, Wentz vs. Cam
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal recap Thursday night's matchup between the Eagles and Panthers (1:00) and look ahead to all of the Week 6 action, including what Zeke's suspension means for the Cowboys (8:00); What Jay Cutler is really doing in Miami (19:00); Wess goes out on a limb for his Lock of the Week (36:00); Plus everything you need to know about the Week 6 games.
